             was indicted for <rs id="t17820515-1-off1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17820515-1-off1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17820515-1-off1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing a saddle, value 3 s. two bridles, value 3 s. three leather collars, value 2 s. a leather portmanteau, value 2 s. a woollen breast-cloth, value 6 d. and a sieve, value 6 d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17820515-1-victim50" type="victimName">
                           William Arthur 
                           Crosby
                        <interp inst="t17820515-1-victim50" type="surname" value="Crosby"></interp>
